  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize moving forward in clear and path_clear situations.",
    "Commit to a single rotation direction when obstacles are detected on the side, avoiding oscillation.",
    "After obstacle_front, always pass through an escape state before resuming forward movement.",
    "When blue_seen is detected, immediately transition to a move_to_blue commit state.",
    "Allow stop only from the move_to_blue commit state.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state to ensure DES completeness.",
    "Commit states ensure that the robot continues its action until a safe or goal condition is met.",
    "Never allow move_forward in response to obstacle_front or immediately after; always use a recovery state.",
